Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}逐渐失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}仍坚信并追逐着光明
